sections.text:
71-5803.11.Nursing facility, defined.

Nursing facility has the same meaning as in section 71-424.

SourceLaws 1991, LB 244, § 11;R.S.1943, (1996), § 71-5809.02;Laws 1997, LB 798, § 15;Laws 2000, LB 819, § 118.
